    "Our sightseeing tour continues as we make our way towards Praça Paris, a nod to Franco-Brazilian friendship, nestled gently amidst the energetic life of Rio. Conceived in the early nineteen twenties, this public square is an area that echoes the meticulous landscaping known to French gardens of the era." /
    "Designed by the esteemed French urbanist Alfred Agache, it is a place where manicured hedges and playful fountains conspire to create an atmosphere of serene peace." /
    "Layers of greenery laid out with precise artistry invite us to roam along the well-maintained paths. Here, sculptures speak silently of cross-continental connections, including the contributions of French artists to this peaceful setting." /
    "Our guide leads us to a spot where the ambient strains of a street performer's music are best heard. With each note, the music wraps around us, a peaceful serenade that beautifully complements the calm exuded by the square." /
    "We witness visitors reclined on benches, losing themselves in the pages of a book or simply lounging in relaxed satisfaction, surrounded by statues that stand as silent guardians of the plaza's elegance." /
    "As the soft hum of the limousine signals our departure, we reflect on the series of experiences that have graced our journey through Rio de Janeiro. Our guide, with his quiet familiarity of every corner and contour of the city, has been our compass and companion." /
    "From the peaks of Corcovado to the historical wonders of downtown, from the creativity of the Selarón Steps to the embrace of Rio's cultural and natural treasures, we have traversed a world that whispers a colorful history and hums with the energy of its people and landscapes. Our hearts are richer for the tales that have unfolded before us, each site a page in Rio's open book." /
    "As we recline in the comfort of the limousine, carrying away with us the memories that have gently imprinted themselves upon our minds, we join the city's evening quiet. Our eyes rest upon the softening sky that cradles the horizon, the stars preparing to make their appearance in the cosmic expanse above." /
    "Rio de Janeiro, with its rhythm, color, and warmth, has shared with us its essence, offering up its beauty and stories with a gentle gesture. As the city lights begin to sparkle, mirroring the first stars, our tour concludes in a grateful silence, an unspoken celebration in all we have encountered in this city of dreams."

  override val start =
    "As we arrive in Rio de Janeiro, the very air seems to breathe a welcoming melody, the gentle introduction to a most exquisite exploration. The city stretches out before us, a scene rich with culture, framed by the rolling Atlantic Ocean and the iconic peaks that reach up to embrace the sky." /
